{"tid":101141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免簽證入境美國的國家不受Trump行政命令影響","createTime":"2017-01-30T15:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T12:28:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"daaf6845356f83d08003c9da0fb15e5f5bbf909d","tid":101141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>媒體誤傳 AIT澄清:<br />\n台人赴美免簽不受川普入境禁令影響</strong><br />\n<br />\n生活中心/綜合報導 2017-01-29 18:00<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普日前針對七個國家實施入境禁令，國內媒體《天下》網站文章，誤把川普命令中宣佈撤銷申請簽證免面談計劃（Visa Interview Waiver Program），當成是包括台灣在內的免簽證計劃（Visa Waiver Program, VWP），影響台灣旅客進入美國的權益。<br />\n<br />\n美國在台協會發言人遊詩雅今天澄清表示，美國國土安全部（DHS）管理的免簽證計畫（VWP），目前沒有任何改變。免簽證計劃（Visa Waiver Program）和簽證免面談計畫（Visa Interview Waiver Program）並非同一回事。台灣人民到美國旅遊還是可以享有VWP待遇，VWP跟「Visa Interview Waiver Program」是不一樣的事情。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國領事事務局（Bureau of Consular Affairs）網站的資訊，<strong>共有38國參與免簽證計劃（VWP），台灣於2012年加入</strong>。符合資格的台灣護照持有人並滿足特定條件，即可赴美從事觀光或商務達90天，無需簽證。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.peoplenews.tw/news/c6d733b2-671e-4197-a5ff-5e49fd00ec7f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2Fc6d733b2-671e-4197-a5ff-5e49fd00ec7f&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cce21fc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.peoplenews.tw/news/c6d733b2-671e-4197-a5ff-5e49fd00ec7f</a>"},{"pid":"e2d7aae0d66276cce26bc23c16a01108a509a008","tid":101141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda25003c3ede9e26714ac2698634c807efb2374","tid":101141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ef874c6fdd02b2ed001f4bd9df94646bdbc90","tid":101141,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"免簽國都係美盟國"},{"pid":"56a3b8fb